Insider Activity


Individual




Steven I. Sarowitz



Mr. Steven I. Sarowitz is Chairman at Paylocity Corp., Chairman at Paylocity Holding Corp., Chief Executive Officer at Blue Marble Payroll LLC, a Manager at Paylocity Management Holdings LLC and a Member at Sierra Club. Mr. Sarowitz was previously employed as President by Independent Payroll Providers Association and a Principal by R.F. White Co., Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Illinois.



