Board of Directors





Steve Sarowitz

As Founder and Chairman, Mr. Sarowitz started Paylocity in 1997 with a small investment and a tremendous vision.




Steve Beauchamp

As President and CEO since 2007, Mr. Beauchamp is accountable for the vision and execution of our entire operation.




